reviewText: This video is incredible. Not only does Sigung ( Master ) Tak Wah Eng give full instruction and tutelage on the "Poon Lung Gim", or 'Double edge Dragon Straight Sword form'. But, also provides various sword sparring drills as well. Helps to break up the boredom and monotony of just practicing the form, over and over again. I highly recommend this video!!!!
